<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>ACS/ACE - Sistema de Saúde</title><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"><link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"><link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"><style>body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0066b3 0%,#003d6b 100%);min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}.login-container{display:flex;width:100%;max-width:1200px;background:white;border-radius:30px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);}.login-left{flex:1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0066b3 0%,#003d6b 100%);padding:60px;color:white;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;}.login-left h1{font-size:42px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:20px;}.login-left p{opacity:0.9;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:40px;}.features{display:flex;gap:30px;}.feature{text-align:center;}.feature i{font-size:36px;margin-bottom:10px;}.login-right{flex:1;padding:60px;}.login-right h2{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#1a3a4f;margin-bottom:10px;}.form-control{border-radius:12px;padding:12px;margin-bottom:15px;width:100%;border:1px solid #dee2e6;}.btn-login{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0066b3 0%,#003d6b 100%);border:none;padding:12px;border-radius:12px;color:white;font-weight:600;width:100%;cursor:pointer;}.demo-info{background:#f8f9fa;padding:15px;border-radius:12px;margin-top:30px;text-align:center;font-size:13px;}@media(max-width:768px){.login-left{display:none;}}</style></head>
<body><div class="login-container"><div class="login-left"><h1>ACS/ACE</h1><p>Plataforma digital para Agentes Comunitários de Saúde e Combate às Endemias</p><div class="features"><div class="feature"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i><span>24/7</span></div><div class="feature"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i><span>GPS</span></div><div class="feature"><i class="fas fa-wifi"></i><span>Offline</span></div></div></div><div class="login-right"><h2>Acesse o Sistema</h2><p>Digite suas credenciais para continuar</p><form id="loginForm"><input type="email" id="email" class="form-control" placeholder="admin@gmail.com" required><input type="password" id="senha" class="form-control" placeholder="admin123" required><button type="submit" class="btn-login">Entrar</button></form><div class="demo-info"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Credenciais<br><strong>Admin:</strong> admin@gmail.com / admin123<br><strong>Supervisor:</strong> supervisor@gmail.com / super123</div><div id="loginError" class="alert alert-danger mt-3" style="display:none"></div></div></div><script>document.getElementById('loginForm').addEventListener('submit', async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const res = await fetch('/api/login', { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify({ email: document.getElementById('email').value, senha: document.getElementById('senha').value }) }); const data = await res.json(); if (data.success) { localStorage.setItem('user', JSON.stringify(data.user)); window.location.href = '/app'; } else { document.getElementById('loginError').style.display = 'block'; document.getElementById('loginError').innerHTML = 'Email ou senha incorretos!'; } });</script></body>
</html>
